    <!-- About — App Description -->
    <string name="about_description">Nexuzy Publisher is an open-source, AI-powered news publishing Android app. It fetches news from RSS feeds, auto-detects categories, rewrites articles using Gemini AI, verifies facts with OpenAI, checks grammar with Sarvam AI, and pushes SEO-ready drafts to WordPress — complete with featured images and category assignment.</string>
    <string name="app_type">Open Source · Free to Use</string>

    <!-- About — Tech Stack -->
    <string name="tools_tech_title">Tools &amp; Technologies</string>
    <string name="tools_tech">Gemini AI (Article Writing) • OpenAI (Fact Verification) • Sarvam AI (Grammar Check) • Firebase Auth &amp; Firestore (Sync &amp; Backup) • WordPress REST API (Publishing) • Room Database • OkHttp • Kotlin Coroutines</string>

